11 March 2009The media briefing of the Governance and Administration (G&amp;A) Cluster on the implementation of the Programme of Action (PoA) scheduled for Thursday, 12 March 2009 has been postponed.The briefing will now take place as follows:Date: Tuesday, 17 March Time: 09h00 to 10h30 Venue: Room 153, Union Buildings, PretoriaThere will be a video link-up to Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town. The Minister of Public Service and Administration, Richard Baloyi will chair the briefing.Enquiries Bongiwe Gambu (Pretoria) Cell: 082 714 9463Colin Cruywagen (Cape Town) Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)